The minimum occurs at one of the four roots of the quartic equation given
 by
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
5a\theta_{i}^{4}+4b\theta_{i}^{3}+3c\theta_{i}^{2}+2d\theta_{i}+e=0
\end{equation}

\end_inset

which can be found by applying the elementary formulae for the roots of
 a quartic equation.
